refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
public intCountable::count
このメソッドは、 count 関数の value パラメーターが Countable を実装している場合に実行されます。

  &reftitle.examples;

   Countable::count の例


<?php

class Counter implements Countable
{
    private $count = 0;

    public function count(): int
    {
        return ++$this->count;
    }
}

$counter = new Counter;

for ($i = 0; $i < 10; ++$i) {
    echo "I have been count()ed " . count($counter) . " times\n";
}

?>


